overview.en: Bitsou is a digital currency investment decision-making tool based on blockchain, artificial intelligence and big data technology. Different from other investment service platforms, Bitsou relies on core data processing technology and its own core algorithms to provide users with intelligent digital currency investment services and comprehensive and convenient information exchange channels.
overview.zh: Bitsou(比特搜)是基于区块链、人工智能、大数据技术的数字货币投资决策工具。区别于其他投资服务平台，Bitsou(比特搜)依托核心数据处理技术和自有核心算法，为用户提供智能的数字货币投资服务和全面、便捷的信息交流渠道。
